 <i>Yeah, a lot.</i>

26:18.827 --> 26:21.371
 <i>Did you know he named you</i>
 <i>his emergency contact?</i>

26:21.413 --> 26:22.747
 <i>No.</i>

26:24.874 --> 26:27.586
 <i>X-rays are preventing me</i>
 <i>from using the airport,</i>

26:27.586 --> 26:30.380
 <i>and I have to get to Seattle.</i>

26:30.422 --> 26:31.923
 <i>He stole it.</i>

26:35.010 --> 26:35.969
 <i>You're an asshole.</i>

26:35.969 --> 26:38.179
