 <i>get it back to the guy.</i>

26:38.179 --> 26:39.639
 <i>They think your friend's</i>
 <i>on some shit</i>

26:39.639 --> 26:40.974
 <i>they don't know about yet.</i>

26:40.974 --> 26:43.518
 <i>He drinks water like a camel.</i>

26:43.518 --> 26:45.645
 <i>I have four stomachs.</i>

26:50.191 --> 26:51.651
 <i>Are they charging him?</i>

26:51.651 --> 26:52.986
 <i>Look, he's the cherry</i>
 <i>on a weird day.</i>

26:53.028 --> 26:56.323
 <i>-A kid puked in the luggage...</i>
 <i>-I have to get to Seattle.</i>

26:56.323 --> 26:58.033
 <i>[paramedic]</i>
 <i>It's the top of a long weekend</i>

26:58.074 --> 26:59.284
 <i>and nobody wants the paperwork.</i>

26:59.284 --> 27:02.329
 <i>-I have to get to Seattle.</i>
 <i>-If you sign for him...</i>

27:02.370 --> 27:03.788
 <i>If you don't,</i>
 <i>he goes to the psych unit,</i>

27:03.830 --> 27:06.082
 <i>he's there a couple of days</i>
 <i>till he gets a full exam.</i>

27:06.124 --> 27:07.542
 <i>I have to get to...</i>

27:07.542 --> 27:08.960
 <i>Stop talking.</i>

27:09.002 --> 27:10.670
 <i>...Seattle.</i>

27:12.422 --> 27:15.759
 <i>Your epinephrine levels</i>
 <i>are vacillating so much</i>

27:15.759 --> 27:18.428
 <i>it is irritating</i>
 <i>my sinus cavities</i>

27:18.428 --> 27:22.682
 <i>and making my scalp itch.</i>
 <i>You need stabilizing.</i>

27:22.724 --> 27:23.725
 <i>You know what? You're right.</i>

27:23.767 --> 27:26.311
 <i>You're right.</i>
 <i>You're totally right.</i>

27:27.437 --> 27:30.649
 <i>Did you come here</i>
 <i>just to leave me?</i>

27:39.658 --> 27:41.701
 <i>Was there a tornado?</i>

27:43.662 --> 27:45.872
 <i>[breath trembling]</i>
 <i>Was that real?</i>

27:46.414 --> 27:47.999
 <i>'Cause, you know,</i>
 <i>the only thing</i>

27:48.041 --> 27:51.461
 <i>that makes sense to me</i>
 <i>is that I was hallucinating...</i>

27:51.503 --> 27:52.879
 <i>It was real.</i>

27:56.716 --> 27:58.802
 <i>Your message was inside it?</i>

27:58.843 --> 28:00.011
 <i>It was.</i>

28:00.553 --> 28:01.846
 <i>From who?</i>

28:02.389 --> 28:03.890
 <i>My adept.</i>

28:04.432 --> 28:06.017
 <i>Thomas Newton?</i>

28:07.185 --> 28:08.770
 <i>How is that possible?</i>

28:08.770 --> 28:11.898
 <i>You cannot understand it yet.</i>

28:12.232 --> 28:15.235
 <i>If we continue, you will.</i>

28:15.610 --> 28:17.195
 <i>No, no, no. No.</i>

28:17.195 --> 28:19.155
 <i>You can be as crazy as you like.</i>

28:19.155 --> 28:21.616
 <i>But I can't be, all right?</i>

28:21.658 --> 28:23.702
 <i>How did you survive that?</i>

28:24.619 --> 28:26.246
 <i>Who are you?</i>

28:26.246 --> 28:27.414
 <i>I am an immigrant.</i>

28:27.414 --> 28:29.624
 <i>No, my father's an immigrant.</i>

28:29.624 --> 28:31.167
 <i>You're... You're a...</i>

28:31.209 --> 28:33.044
 <i>From Anthea.</i>

28:35.880 --> 28:36.923
 <i>I...</i>

28:37.632 --> 28:39.426
 <i>I saw your face.</i>

28:40.719 --> 28:43.471
 <i>Your real face. I saw it.</i>

28:43.513 --> 28:48.017
 <i>I am talking to someone</i>
 <i>from another planet.</i>

28:48.852 --> 28:50.353
 <i>So am I.</i>

28:51.271 --> 28:54.274
 <i>[whimpering] Jesus Christ.</i>

28:58.987 --> 29:00.864
 <i>[breathes heavily]</i>

29:03.158 --> 29:05.410
 <i>I received my instructions.</i>

29:06.119 --> 29:08.288
 <i>I understand my next step.</i>

