30:41.130 --> 30:43.842
 <i>This is all I have left.</i>

30:45.969 --> 30:47.136
 <i>Look,</i>

30:47.679 --> 30:51.015
 <i>I'm gonna pick up my dad</i>
 <i>and my daughter,</i>

30:51.432 --> 30:53.393
 <i>and then, I don't know, I'll...</i>

30:53.434 --> 30:55.562
