34:49.670 --> 34:52.298
 <i>Is there a decades-long task</i>

34:52.298 --> 34:57.261
 <i>you must complete before</i>
 <i>you are permitted to die?</i>

34:57.261 --> 34:58.721
 <i>Oh, Jesus.</i>

34:58.721 --> 35:00.264
 <i>I am so sorry, everyone.</i>

35:00.306 --> 35:01.933
 <i>-I'm so sorry.</i>
