35:01.933 --> 35:04.310
 <i>You store your aged</i>
 <i>and forget about them.</i>

35:04.310 --> 35:07.814
 <i>Why expend planetary</i>
 <i>resources when a peaceful,</i>

35:07.814 --> 35:10.608
 <i>well-planned death</i>
 <i>would be efficient?</i>

35:10.650 --> 35:13.111
 <i>[chuckles] I like</i>
 <i>that boy's thinking.</i>

35:13.111 --> 35:15.321
 <i>Whose mandate is this?</i>

35:15.321 --> 35:17.115
 <i>[radio tuning]</i>

35:23.412 --> 35:26.833
 <i>You are a pupa.</i>

35:27.166 --> 35:31.087
 <i>You're a larva. Larva.</i>

35:31.087 --> 35:33.464
 <i>Molly Molls. Stop staring.</i>

35:34.674 --> 35:37.802
 <i>She is taking me to Seattle.</i>

35:37.802 --> 35:40.012
 <i>I'm taking you</i>
 <i>to the bus station.</i>

35:40.012 --> 35:40.847
 <i>Who's hungry?</i>

35:40.888 --> 35:42.640
 <i>I had mac and cheese for lunch.</i>

35:42.682 --> 35:46.644
 <i>I had an amino acid pack</i>
 <i>before impact.</i>

35:46.686 --> 35:48.771
 <i>[radio jockey]</i> <i>1-888-Car-Talk.</i>

35:48.813 --> 35:49.772
 <i>Ah.</i>

35:49.772 --> 35:52.108
<i>That's 1-888-227-8255.</i>
