35:52.150 --> 35:54.443
 <i>No. This is my show.</i>

35:54.443 --> 35:57.280
 <i>-[indistinct radio chatter]</i>
 <i>-Change the frequency,</i>

35:57.280 --> 35:59.240
 <i>-please.</i>
 <i>-Are you the radio sheriff?</i>

35:59.282 --> 36:00.616
 <i>Okay, do I have to stop</i>
 <i>this truck?</i>

36:00.658 --> 36:03.035
 <i>You have already</i>
 <i>stopped the truck.</i>

36:03.077 --> 36:05.079
 <i>You're in trouble, Grandpa.</i>

36:05.121 --> 36:06.789
 <i>I prefer music.</i>

36:06.831 --> 36:07.957
<i>[</i> <i>Papa Was a Rolling Stone</i>
