36:14.005 --> 36:15.214
 <i>Just listen.</i>

36:15.256 --> 36:17.175
 <i>[sInging along]</i>
<i>Yes, I will</i>

36:17.175 --> 36:20.011
<i>'Cause that was the day</i>

36:20.052 --> 36:23.306
<i>That my daddy died</i>

