 <i> slow suspenseful</i>
 <i>music playing </i>

37:47.598 --> 37:48.933
 <i>[device beeps softly]</i>

37:54.397 --> 37:57.316
 <i> slow suspenseful</i>
 <i>music continues </i>

38:00.569 --> 38:02.488
 <i>[objects tinkling]</i>

38:05.116 --> 38:06.325
 <i>[panting]</i>

