 <i> ominous music playing </i>

38:36.188 --> 38:37.940
 <i>[dragging]</i>

38:48.868 --> 38:50.870
 <i>[fire crackling]</i>

38:53.789 --> 38:55.499
 <i>[flies buzzing]</i>

