40:56.662 --> 40:59.123
 <i>Where do you think my girls</i>
 <i>get it from, hmm?</i>

41:00.207 --> 41:03.002
 <i>The Nerd Farm brought</i>
 <i>Grandpa from the Bahamas,</i>

41:03.043 --> 41:04.920
 <i>'cause he's a super genius.</i>

41:04.962 --> 41:06.881
 <i>God bless the Nerds!</i>

41:06.881 --> 41:07.965
 <i>Mom worked there, too.</i>

41:07.965 --> 41:12.553
 <i>The Los Alamos</i>
 <i>National Laboratory.</i>

41:12.553 --> 41:15.347
 <i>Your field was particle physics.</i>

41:15.347 --> 41:18.601
 <i>Her doctoral dissertation</i>
 <i>evolved your work.</i>

41:18.642 --> 41:23.230
 <i>She is quantifiably</i>
 <i>more intelligent.</i>

41:23.230 --> 41:24.273
 <i>[laughs]</i>

41:24.315 --> 41:27.693
 <i>How much more?</i>
 <i>Is there a percentage?</i>

41:27.735 --> 41:29.111
 <i>Twenty-six.</i>

41:29.528 --> 41:30.988
 <i>Did you tell him to say that?</i>

41:31.030 --> 41:34.742
 <i>Yeah, I did. [chuckles]</i>

41:34.742 --> 41:36.160
 <i>She's brilliant.</i>

41:36.202 --> 41:39.246
 <i>No matter how she feels,</i>
 <i>she's brilliant!</i>

41:39.288 --> 41:42.791
 <i>A flawed path does not</i>
 <i>make that any less true.</i>

41:42.791 --> 41:44.001
 <i>Everyone makes mistakes.</i>

41:44.043 --> 41:47.129
 <i>[Faraday] What flaws?</i>
 <i>What mistakes?</i>

41:47.129 --> 41:48.464
 <i>You have a bus to catch.</i>

41:48.506 --> 41:51.592
 <i>[Faraday] It'll be faster</i>
 <i>if you drive me to Seattle.</i>

41:51.634 --> 41:53.469
 <i>[Justin] Yeah,</i>
 <i>but I'm not going to.</i>

41:53.511 --> 41:55.137
 <i>We're gonna eat, quick.</i>

41:55.137 --> 41:57.848
 <i>We haven't had company</i>
 <i>for four or five years.</i>

41:58.557 --> 42:01.685
 <i>There is a bird in the dogsled.</i>

42:01.685 --> 42:03.896
 <i>Dad, you are not allowed</i>
 <i>to like him.</i>

42:03.896 --> 42:04.688
 <i>It's too late.</i>

42:04.730 --> 42:07.566
 <i>Maybe there's a dog</i>
 <i>in the bird-sled.</i>

42:09.527 --> 42:11.237
 <i>Are you a radical theorist?</i>

42:11.237 --> 42:13.197
 <i>Are you gonna eat your fries?</i>

42:13.197 --> 42:15.741
 <i>You are a formidable pupa.</i>

42:20.371 --> 42:21.830
 <i>Hmm.</i>

42:21.830 --> 42:26.168
 <i>Wash away my iniquity</i>
 <i>and cleanse me of my sin.</i>

42:26.168 --> 42:27.545
 <i>[continues mumbling</i>
 <i>indistinctly]</i>

42:27.586 --> 42:29.296
 <i>[Spencer] Hey, I can, um...</i>

42:29.338 --> 42:31.715
 <i>I can tell you</i>
 <i>everything I know.</i>

42:31.715 --> 42:32.758
 <i>Uh...</i>

42:33.968 --> 42:35.135
 <i>It's... It's not much, but...</i>

42:35.177 --> 42:38.847
 <i>But maybe</i>
 <i>it'll help us relax.</i>

42:38.889 --> 42:41.058
 <i>[continues mumbling]</i>

42:41.058 --> 42:42.017
 <i>Okay, sir?</i>

42:42.059 --> 42:44.144
 <i>I came here</i>
 <i>'cause there was, uh...</i>

42:44.186 --> 42:46.897
 <i>Uh, a signal in a tornado</i>

42:46.939 --> 42:49.400
 <i>about 48 hours ago. Okay?</i>

42:49.441 --> 42:53.279
 <i>And your name,</i>
 <i>it was attached to a file.</i>

42:53.279 --> 42:55.447
 <i>The signal was bi-directional.</i>

42:55.489 --> 42:57.616
 <i>Which... It's... It...</i>
 <i>It's like there's two...</i>

42:57.658 --> 42:59.618
 <i>There's two people talking.</i>

42:59.660 --> 43:02.746
 <i>Does that mean anything to you?</i>

43:03.914 --> 43:05.291
 <i>Two people?</i>

43:06.500 --> 43:08.794
 <i>Two people.</i>

43:12.506 --> 43:13.674
 <i>I'm just trying to figure out</i>

43:13.674 --> 43:15.801
 <i>why that signal pinged your file</i>

43:15.801 --> 43:19.680
 <i>from 45 years ago, man.</i>
 <i>[breathes heavily]</i>

43:19.680 --> 43:21.807
 <i>That's when we first heard it!</i>

43:23.183 --> 43:25.644
 <i>He was trying to send a message.</i>

43:27.062 --> 43:29.773
 <i>I guess someone</i>
 <i>finally answered.</i>

43:31.567 --> 43:33.277
 <i>Who? What message?</i>

43:33.277 --> 43:35.321
 <i>[yells] You are so fucked!</i>

43:35.321 --> 43:37.323
 <i>They just sent you,</i>
 <i>they sent you like</i>

43:37.323 --> 43:40.034
 <i>one of those Airedale dogs</i>
 <i>in World War I,</i>

43:40.034 --> 43:41.410
 <i>running between the trenches.</i>

43:41.452 --> 43:43.120
 <i>Good boy, good boy.</i>

43:43.120 --> 43:45.539
 <i>Or a German Shepherd</i>
 <i>out in space,</i>

43:45.539 --> 43:46.999
 <i>or a monkey on a rocket!</i>

43:47.041 --> 43:49.376
 <i>A monkey can be a cosmonaut</i>

43:49.418 --> 43:52.338
 <i>'cause they didn't tell him</i>
 <i>he's gonna die.</i>

43:53.047 --> 43:54.965
 <i>You're gonna die.</i>

43:54.965 --> 43:56.800
 <i>Or you're gonna want to,</i>

43:57.343 --> 44:02.681
 <i>after what they make you do.</i>
 <i>[sobbing]</i>

44:02.723 --> 44:06.310
 <i>I thought insurance</i>
 <i>would keep me alive.</i>

44:06.602 --> 44:08.270
 <i>That fucking film!</i>

44:08.312 --> 44:09.647
 <i>That's what you came for.</i>

44:09.647 --> 44:13.108
 <i>I have no fucking clue what</i>
 <i>you're talking about, man.</i>

44:13.150 --> 44:15.027
 <i>-What film?</i>
 <i>-[crying]</i>

44:15.027 --> 44:16.779
 <i>He was sweet.</i>

44:18.113 --> 44:21.241
 <i>He was so sweet. Newton.</i>

44:21.283 --> 44:24.620
 <i>His face, an angel.</i>

44:24.620 --> 44:26.747
 <i>He was like an angel.</i>

44:26.747 --> 44:28.666
 <i>It's still fucking looking at me</i>

44:28.666 --> 44:30.376
 <i>when I close my eyes.</i>

44:30.376 --> 44:33.587
 <i>Nothing gets rid of it.</i>
 <i>Not even prayer.</i>

44:33.587 --> 44:36.173
 <i>But, just... Who...</i>
 <i>Who are you talking about?</i>

44:36.173 --> 44:37.508
 <i>Who's Newton?</i>

44:37.508 --> 44:39.301
 <i>We took his eyes out.</i>

44:40.010 --> 44:41.887
 <i>We made him a psychopath.</i>

44:42.221 --> 44:43.972
 <i>We did that.</i>

44:43.972 --> 44:45.349
 <i>-I did that!</i>
 <i>-Hey.</i>

44:45.349 --> 44:47.976
 <i>-No. No, no way, Dr. Papel.</i>
 <i>-[sobbing]</i>

44:47.976 --> 44:51.605
 <i>You... You did your job, okay?</i>
 <i>You did your job.</i>

44:51.605 --> 44:52.564
 <i>And that's okay.</i>

44:52.564 --> 44:55.484
 <i>But tell me,</i>
 <i>who are you talking about?</i>

44:55.526 --> 44:58.028
 <i>And what insurance?</i>

44:58.404 --> 44:59.863
 <i>What film?</i>

44:59.905 --> 45:03.325
 <i>I sure learned</i>
 <i>what's inside me. I sure did.</i>

45:03.367 --> 45:07.204
 <i>This ends now.</i>
 <i>One monkey to another.</i>

45:07.246 --> 45:09.248
 <i>I won't let you do it again.</i>

45:09.248 --> 45:11.458
 <i>-No one will survive it!</i>
 <i>-Okay, fuckin' wait!</i>

45:11.500 --> 45:13.043
 <i>Wait, wait, wait!</i>

45:13.043 --> 45:16.755
 <i>Dr. Papel, wait, please.</i>

45:17.923 --> 45:18.716
 <i>Please.</i>

45:18.757 --> 45:22.344
 <i>I just go.</i>
 <i>I go where they send me, okay?</i>

45:22.344 --> 45:24.763
 <i>Hell is where we're going.</i>

45:26.557 --> 45:27.850
 <i>[groans]</i>

45:29.893 --> 45:31.353
 <i>[grunts]</i>

45:31.770 --> 45:34.440
 <i> tense music playing </i>

45:35.315 --> 45:37.359
 <i>[both grunting]</i>

45:42.740 --> 45:46.285
 <i>I took his eyes! He's insane!</i>

45:46.326 --> 45:48.871
 <i>He's insane!</i>
 <i>Do you know what that means?</i>

45:50.205 --> 45:51.457
 <i>Yeah.</i>

45:52.040 --> 45:56.754
 <i>No. No. You don't.</i>

45:58.464 --> 46:00.674
 <i>And now there's another one.</i>

46:00.716 --> 46:05.304
 <i>Oh, God, I am so fucking tired.</i>

46:05.304 --> 46:08.307
 <i>You got no idea</i>
 <i>what's coming to you.</i>

46:08.348 --> 46:09.558
 <i>[shotgun fires]</i>

46:09.558 --> 46:11.810
 <i>-[body thuds]</i>
 <i>-[breathing heavily]</i>

46:19.485 --> 46:21.153
<i>[Josiah]</i> <i>Dear God in Heaven.</i>

46:21.195 --> 46:25.115
 <i>- soft piano music playing </i>
 <i>-You have your mysteries.</i>

46:25.157 --> 46:27.910
 <i>You've made us to be flawed.</i>

46:28.494 --> 46:32.873
 <i>In our flaws,</i>
 <i>we see our possibilities.</i>

46:32.873 --> 46:37.711
 <i>In our flaws, we see your mercy.</i>

46:37.753 --> 46:39.838
 <i>We see your wisdom.</i>

46:39.880 --> 46:43.217
 <i>We see who you want us to be</i>

46:43.217 --> 46:45.385
 <i>and who we can be.</i>

46:45.385 --> 46:48.430
 <i>We thank you</i>
 <i>for the opportunities</i>

46:48.472 --> 46:50.641
 <i>for us to discover ourselves</i>

46:50.682 --> 46:55.229
 <i>through our mistakes.</i>
 <i>We're humble in your presence.</i>

46:55.270 --> 46:57.147
 <i>Grateful, Almighty.</i>

46:57.981 --> 46:59.441
 <i>Amen.</i>

47:00.108 --> 47:02.027
 <i>-Amen.</i>
 <i>-Amen.</i>

47:04.321 --> 47:07.950
 <i>Who are you talking to?</i>

47:09.868 --> 47:10.953
 <i>Most times, it's the Lord,</i>

47:10.994 --> 47:14.164
 <i>but I heard him say it</i>
 <i>about Tina Turner.</i>

47:14.164 --> 47:17.167
 <i>[all laughing]</i>

47:17.876 --> 47:20.337
 <i>What are the mysteries?</i>

47:20.379 --> 47:22.422
 <i>Things people don't know.</i>

47:22.464 --> 47:23.882
 <i>You are a scientist.</i>

47:23.882 --> 47:27.177
 <i>How can you allow that to be?</i>

47:28.053 --> 47:32.057
 <i>Allowing it to be</i>
 <i>makes me a scientist.</i>

47:32.099 --> 47:34.476
 <i>You're not supposed</i>
 <i>to know everything.</i>

47:34.476 --> 47:36.603
 <i>That is right.</i>
 <i>That's the truth.</i>

47:36.645 --> 47:40.399
 <i>Are you afraid to take me</i>
 <i>where I have to go?</i>

47:40.816 --> 47:42.526
 <i>-What?</i>
 <i>-[Faraday] I smell it.</i>

47:42.526 --> 47:45.320
 <i>The amygdala response</i>
 <i>in your brain was triggered</i>

47:45.320 --> 47:49.533
 <i>when Josiah said</i>
 <i>things go astray.</i>

47:49.533 --> 47:52.911
 <i>Maybe you're smelling the cow</i>
 <i>we're eating right now.</i>

47:52.953 --> 47:56.874
<i>Nowhere to run</i>
<i>Nowhere to hide </i>

47:56.874 --> 47:58.625
 <i>[Molly] My mom</i>
 <i>doesn't get afraid.</i>

47:58.667 --> 48:01.378
 <i>Or if she does,</i>
 <i>she does it anyway.</i>

48:01.378 --> 48:03.922
 <i>-Yeah.</i>
 <i>-Well, things do go astray.</i>

48:03.922 --> 48:07.217
 <i>One little cell went astray</i>
 <i>in my body</i>

48:07.259 --> 48:08.594
 <i>and caused all...</i>

48:09.678 --> 48:11.555
 <i>Caused all this...</i>

48:11.805 --> 48:13.307
 <i>I am aware.</i>

48:13.307 --> 48:15.142
 <i>I like your cells.</i>

48:15.183 --> 48:16.518
 <i>Mm-hmm.</i>

48:16.518 --> 48:19.187
 <i>It's frightening</i>
 <i>when in one moment,</i>

48:19.229 --> 48:20.522
 <i>everything changes.</i>

48:20.564 --> 48:22.816
 <i>And you get jammed up</i>
 <i>and caught up</i>

48:22.816 --> 48:25.861
 <i>and you have to explain</i>
 <i>your whole damn life!</i>

48:25.861 --> 48:27.654
 <i>-Dad?</i>
 <i>-She was a world changer.</i>

48:27.696 --> 48:30.449
 <i>You know how many</i>
 <i>come along in a generation?</i>

48:30.449 --> 48:31.700
 <i>-One.</i>
 <i>-Hey, Dad? Dad?</i>

48:31.700 --> 48:34.578
 <i>-[Molly breathing heavily]</i>
 <i>-The pupa is afraid as well.</i>

48:34.578 --> 48:35.996
 <i>Don't talk about my child,</i>
 <i>please.</i>

48:36.038 --> 48:40.292
 <i>No faith!</i>
 <i>A white girl would never...</i>

48:40.292 --> 48:42.044
 <i>White girl would've cried.</i>

48:42.044 --> 48:44.087
 <i>She would've been given</i>
 <i>a hanky and a cookie.</i>

48:44.129 --> 48:47.883
 <i>They made her defend herself.</i>
 <i>We had to defend her!</i>

48:47.925 --> 48:50.093
 <i>-Defend her from what?</i>
 <i>-Dad, you're freaking her out.</i>

48:50.135 --> 48:51.929
 <i>Molly, come sit with me, baby.</i>
 <i>Come on.</i>

48:51.970 --> 48:53.388
 <i>You're a world changer!</i>

48:53.388 --> 48:55.349
 <i>-Stop it! Stop!</i>
 <i>-My stomach hurts.</i>

48:55.349 --> 48:57.100
 <i>-Molly? Molly.</i>
 <i>-Oh.</i>

48:57.768 --> 48:58.644
 <i>It's time for you to go.</i>

48:58.685 --> 49:01.271
 <i>She is not</i>
 <i>utilizing her purpose.</i>

49:01.271 --> 49:03.857
 <i>-You think I don't know that?</i>
 <i>-Hey, we're leaving.</i>

49:03.899 --> 49:05.275
 <i>You have to take me to...</i>

49:05.275 --> 49:06.234
 <i>I don't. I have to work.</i>

49:06.234 --> 49:10.489
 <i>The equation is ill-conceived.</i>
 <i>I have purpose,</i>

49:10.489 --> 49:12.908
 <i>you and Molly have potential.</i>

49:12.950 --> 49:14.868
 <i>Josiah has neither.</i>

49:14.910 --> 49:16.286
 <i>You mind your mouth, boy.</i>

49:16.286 --> 49:17.663
 <i>He does not need you.</i>

49:17.663 --> 49:19.915
 <i>You can place him</i>
 <i>with the others until...</i>

49:19.915 --> 49:21.124
 <i>Don't say that out loud.</i>

49:21.166 --> 49:23.961
 <i>-[Molly] Mom, my stomach hurts.</i>
 <i>-I'll be right there, Molly.</i>

49:23.961 --> 49:26.588
 <i>[Faraday] Josiah, it is clear</i>

49:26.588 --> 49:28.715
 <i>that you have exceeded</i>

49:28.715 --> 49:31.593
 <i>any usefulness</i>
 <i>you ever possessed.</i>

49:31.593 --> 49:36.098
 <i>A final useful act</i>
 <i>would be for you to die now</i>

49:36.139 --> 49:39.101
 <i>and free Justin</i>
 <i>to realize her potential.</i>

49:39.101 --> 49:42.312
 <i>I take care of him, okay?</i>
 <i>End of fucking story.</i>

49:42.354 --> 49:44.523
 <i>-Juzzie!</i>
 <i>-Get up. Get up.</i>

49:44.523 --> 49:46.274
 <i>Go wait outside.</i>

49:46.316 --> 49:47.317
 <i>Juzzie.</i>

49:49.695 --> 49:52.280
 <i>He's telling us</i>
 <i>God's truth, you know.</i>

49:56.827 --> 49:58.203
 <i>[door closes]</i>

49:59.162 --> 50:00.330
 <i>Mom?</i>

50:02.374 --> 50:04.209
 <i>Get in and wait.</i>

50:05.585 --> 50:07.504
 <i>Mommy, my stomach really hurts.</i>

50:07.546 --> 50:08.630
 <i>Oh, I know, baby.</i>

50:08.672 --> 50:11.049
 <i>Portia's gonna take care</i>
 <i>of you till I get back, okay?</i>

50:11.091 --> 50:13.510
 <i>-[Molly] For how long?</i>
 <i>-Real quick, baby.</i>

50:13.510 --> 50:16.054
 <i>[windchimes tinkling]</i>

50:17.431 --> 50:19.641
 <i>-[TV playing]</i>
 <i>-[Justin] Portia!</i>

50:19.975 --> 50:21.643
 <i>[knocking on door]</i>

50:22.602 --> 50:24.062
 <i>Twenty minutes?</i>

50:24.312 --> 50:25.147
 <i>Sure. No problem.</i>

50:25.188 --> 50:27.232
 <i>I'll be right back,</i>
 <i>okay, baby?</i>

50:29.943 --> 50:31.361
 <i>Hey, you hungry?</i>

50:34.406 --> 50:36.366
 <i>[metal creaking]</i>

50:47.085 --> 50:49.713
 <i> uneasy music playing </i>

50:51.381 --> 50:53.091
 <i>[tinkling]</i>

50:57.804 --> 51:00.182
 <i>[indistinct sports</i>
 <i>commentary on TV]</i>

51:01.266 --> 51:02.684
 <i>[snoring]</i>

51:03.727 --> 51:05.979
<i>[commentator]</i> <i>...have</i>
<i>their work cut out for them.</i>

51:06.021 --> 51:06.938
<i>And look at that.</i>

51:06.938 --> 51:09.316
<i>The ball rockets off</i>
<i>the bat of...</i>

51:09.316 --> 51:12.110
 <i>[commentary continues</i>
 <i>indistinctly on TV]</i>

51:25.415 --> 51:27.292
 <i>[door creaking softly]</i>

51:44.810 --> 51:47.312
 <i> uneasy music continues </i>

51:53.860 --> 51:54.736
 <i>[static]</i>

51:54.778 --> 51:56.363
 <i>[TV commentary glitching]</i>

51:56.363 --> 51:57.739
 <i>[breathes shakily]</i>

51:58.281 --> 52:01.118
 <i>[TV commentary</i>
 <i>continues glitching]</i>

52:02.119 --> 52:04.746
 <i> uneasy music continues </i>

52:12.546 --> 52:14.840
 <i>[TV commentary resumes normally]</i>

52:23.140 --> 52:25.767
 <i>[electricity crackling]</i>

52:26.810 --> 52:27.853
 <i>[static]</i>

52:32.107 --> 52:34.484
 <i>[music plays on car radio]</i>

52:35.110 --> 52:36.653
 <i>[crackling continues]</i>

52:36.695 --> 52:38.864
 <i>[straining]</i>

52:39.948 --> 52:42.200
 <i>[groaning]</i>

52:44.244 --> 52:47.205
 <i> dramatic music playing </i>

53:00.135 --> 53:03.180
 <i>-[crackling stops]</i>
 <i>-[panting]</i>

53:06.474 --> 53:09.811
 <i>Oh, my... [gasping]</i>

53:09.811 --> 53:13.190
 <i>[speaking breathlessly</i>
 <i>and indistinctly]</i>

53:17.694 --> 53:19.070
 <i>Juzzie.</i>

53:19.070 --> 53:20.864
 <i>[Justin gasping]</i>

53:23.658 --> 53:28.413
 <i>[mumbling]</i>
 <i>Oh, my God. Dad. Dad.</i>

53:29.748 --> 53:31.833
 <i>[both whimper]</i>

53:32.792 --> 53:35.378
 <i>[Justin laughs]</i>

53:36.213 --> 53:38.840
 <i>[strained groaning]</i>

53:39.549 --> 53:41.218
 <i>[Faraday] Ow.</i>

53:41.551 --> 53:44.262
 <i>[strained groaning]</i>

53:46.264 --> 53:51.519
 <i>[strained]</i>
 <i>Can we go to Seattle</i>

53:52.896 --> 53:53.939
 <i>now?</i>

53:59.694 --> 54:02.239
 <i> instrumental music playing </i>
